{"tid":1870693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[屯馬線開幕] 2月14日一齊著白色衫去搭佢頭班車","createTime":"2020-02-09T04:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T15:40:10.000Z","uid":45910,"like":68,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e993b4bf320fc868568cf7e42378b9d226976df0","tid":1870693,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"2月14日屯馬線開幕，黨鐵有驚喜，我地都有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人提議全部人一齊著白色衫去搭佢頭班車<br />\n黨鐵影d相出黎，張張都好似721咁，你話點post出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過老實講，我都係想大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好</span>響應<br />\n如果各位鍵盤戰士只係推完post唔實行的話，個站都可能會佈重防<br />\n如果黨鐵影d相出黎，張張都係防暴，好似仲核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊只要推post，公就我地贏，字就黨鐵輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26516ff0ed4e4885bdabfcbda3fe1424bdcc817e","tid":1870693,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"推完再諗做唔做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41470bad19669a94ae8d18cad35dd1c2a91baca","tid":1870693,"uid":5191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"🤔"},{"pid":"caeabc5c628485550e73efec4840aba63891c429","tid":1870693,"uid":4739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"真係開到車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a10076cb096a4a7f5029e91d51560a5ef30191f","tid":1870693,"uid":52188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"你咁做，會唔會畀機會藍絲話你地其實就係白衣人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8928e85b8c29e8d75